Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A sniper shot from outside the window...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:39.09,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A rifle...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:41.92,0:00:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They got to Nezu!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't sense any shadows.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A shadow bullet didn't kill ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a real rifle bullet.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.22,0:00:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake to let Nezu be alone!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.36,0:01:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He went beyond yer detection range.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:03.43,0:01:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:05.57,0:01:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They found out that Nezu was our sniper.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.85,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed they'd come directly fer me!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.18,0:01:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I thought they wanted to capture ya alive?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just loop, so why'd they kill ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.01,0:01:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably figured it out because Haine is looping alongside me.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:34.28,0:01:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya that the starting point gets later each time.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.75,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.56,0:01:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My limit is getting close.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.47,0:01:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The ledge of time is slowly but surely crumbling.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.42,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get killed at the same time, most likely...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only loop one more time.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.02,0:01:59.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:18.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's come to the point where I just want to hoard all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:24.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Even the ramblings from your travels are treasures to me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:27.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Whether I sketch or erase it's all torn away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.49,0:02:31.04,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That's the price I pay for my awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:36.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or my daydream's tricking me and I'm still lost in the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:39.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Illuminated by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Your figure casts a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:46.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}And when that silhouette wavers slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That happens to be my cue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I wish this were fiction but slow motion is how it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:01.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}If the visceral warmth and traces you left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:07.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Are protecting someone's future, I'll play the warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:11.50,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Amidst pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I'll conquer my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:17.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's a paradox of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or perhaps god's algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:23.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}When our tactics overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:28.53,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}We'll be laughing
