Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.92,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back past the limit, so this is the starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:52.30,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554,405)\fscx81\fscy81\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&HF8F9FB&\blur1\fad(687,0)}Death
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.79,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time, I died at 7:55 p.m., \Nand my starting point was 6:40 p.m.
