Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The limit moves forward as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:05.57,0:04:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The limit can't catch up to me now\N since it still moves slower than I do,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.82,0:04:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but it gets faster each time I die.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.05,0:04:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya die now, when's the next starting point?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.58,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, based on the past...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe a little past seven o'clock.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a few minutes ago!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.48,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I die any earlier than the last time, I probably won't get a ninth loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.93,signs,,0,0,0,,{=1}{\move(1268,257,1082.22,187.19,24,2944)\fscx85\fscy85\frz1.51\fax-0.09\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&HF7F7F7&\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5\t(24,2944,\fscx69.81)\t(24,2944,\fscy69.81)}Limit
