Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm treading in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:38.93,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(303,72)\fscx61\fscy61\fax0.11\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&HE9E8F3&\alpha&HB0&\blur7.5}Death
