Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the limit will pass me by.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be anything to return to.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would fall into the darkness below.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.36,0:04:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are ya serious?! It's not just yer imagination?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He saw it as an observer.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be true.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That cliff is an event horizon.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If he falls, his death is fixed.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.31,0:05:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The world Haine sees after that will become reality.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.21,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine realized that and came to kill you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd they find me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.19,0:05:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine may've discovered our strategy in the fourth loop.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:24.14,0:05:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've been scanned when I \Nwas fatally wounded at the end.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.02,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've read my memory leading up to it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.51,0:05:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How do shadows exchange information?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they show their memories the same way yer doing it?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.49,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they can also talk or write.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine also uses telepathy.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.04,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows experience pseudo loops like we do if they come in contact with Haine.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Data is passed through loops, ain't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could they have copied my rifle?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, this place ain't safe.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.51,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A copied item will disappear if it's too far from the shadow who printed it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.20,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Copied items can't exist beyond a \N50-meter radius from the shadow.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.08,0:06:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So a bullet from the copied sniper rifle will only have a 50-meter range.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.83,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an unlimited supply of bullets would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.02,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy won last time, but we also learned a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.23,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This mark means Haine knows where I am.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine will definitely come here to watch me die.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this here tonight.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.88,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming at ya head-on.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya have quite a large entourage, Shide.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.65,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gathered many to your side too, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.45,0:07:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see 'em here, so they must be hiding.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a trap?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.91,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like y'all!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't use any underhanded tricks.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:31.81,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop playing games and fight face-to-face.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound so confident.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.53,0:07:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be our pleasure.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Mio?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin doesn't disappoint.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they're after my life, then I'll be the bait!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to a face-to-face fight?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya taking Shin?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ajiro Shinpei,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,yer quite the rat.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That shadow called Shide has no weakness.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it invincible?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.66,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy and Daddy, come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll go after Shinpei and Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.39,0:09:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finish the hunter, Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.31,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Mother.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.85,0:09:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably won't be able to hear me now,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.30,0:09:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I forgot to tell you something important, Ryuunosuke.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.39,0:09:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer turn!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my shadow!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... Crap!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.56,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dumb, Brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You get so fired up easily.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.46,0:10:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Rosencrantz.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.26,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gildenstern.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.81,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go crazy.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Be as quiet as an explosion.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.11,0:10:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hizuru...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Asa!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Go left.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That bullet should've hit.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I told ya he'd take a hit fer 'em.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.83,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuu...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.64,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can see how I move two seconds into the future!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now shoot!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezu!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.45,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man doesn't even need the scope. He's quite the shot.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya okay, Shide?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and hide where he can't see you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.54,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.03,0:11:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking Mio so long?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiko?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush it, Gil.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yer boss is no longer Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Tokiko.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kill Tokiko!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haine?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That stray shadow's link with me is cut off.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can do that is...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.51,0:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.47,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If that pissed ya off, I dare ya to come and get me!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.63,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this yer doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.36,0:12:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they're certainly making this fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a graceful body.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ya always were athletic, Mio.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.51,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, how I'd love to keep watching ya move, but unfortunately...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Sou!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.19,0:13:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted a face-to-face fight. Such lies.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.32,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sad. I believed you too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually quite the trusting type.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.73,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew ya'd chase me, even if ya knew it was a trap.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer just that cocky!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So ya think yer above all of us?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei is even higher!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.98,0:14:38.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.94,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.94,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.33,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sea of gasoline flames.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's working.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.44,0:14:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shadows really are weak to fire!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.69,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mommy and Daddy. I know it's hot.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.68,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll all go back to normal after I kill him!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, ya goddamn shadow freak!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If yer gonna try to get a bird's-eye view,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,don't take yer eyes off the prize, Haine!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fer Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.52,0:15:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.04,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit messing around with Shiori's body,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.63,0:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ya fake!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.61,0:16:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't erase me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose this body.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.83,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home as her and be with her family forever.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.73,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine! C-Crying won't work on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't erase me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still alive!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.85,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't kill me with f-fire!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But y-you will die!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I w-was th-thinking.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.88,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You and Haine carry d-data into the n-next loop, d-don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.30,0:17:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That means y-you carry injuries and d-death too!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.87,0:17:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It'll take a f-few minutes for Shinpei to d-die.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure not to hit his vitals.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.32,0:17:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What happens if y-you die b-before him?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.93,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so c-curious to d-discover the answer!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.48,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.53,0:18:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I ain't interested in yer "experiment."
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on dying!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How smooth.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.95,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I d-didn't notice you changing p-places.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.24,0:18:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I g-grabbed a dummy p-printed on a lock of hair.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer not invincible.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase ya!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.20,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A human hand!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone's inside it!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.35,0:18:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The flames disappeared.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.71,0:19:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.28,0:19:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ya do...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.71,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They ran away.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to erasing it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.55,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shide, are ya okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I can mold myself back together.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's Mommy and Daddy?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinpei is fatally wounded.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.84,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll die soon and the final loop will begin.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.88,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.19,0:20:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just tired after copying so much.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But yer bleeding.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so tough.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.36,0:20:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This blood is just from some glass touching my true form.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind me, yer wounds are serious!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.51,0:20:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A bulletproof vest.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I found how to make it online.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! That hurts! Stop!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My shoulder and side still got shot!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.64,0:21:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A flame caused by copied gasoline and matches is just data.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.33,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio chose what burns by it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't harm the building nor us.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire was effective on shadows.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows made by Shide died instantly.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.50,0:21:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It also slowed down Shide's movement.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.93,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, Ushio's hacking helped us \Nlearn that someone is inside Shide's body.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.51,0:21:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Haine scanned the air in the gymnasium and erased it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.97,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside air gushed into the building, allowing them to escape.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.32,0:21:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio was unable to scan Shide's true identity.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:00.52,0:22:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The air, though? How in the world...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.45,0:22:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We can copy liquids and gases too.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:06.61,0:22:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It just needs to be in some container.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.24,0:22:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to copy the gasoline in the gas can.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.03,0:22:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you consider the gymnasium a container, it is possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:19.16,0:22:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say it, but it's impressive.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:21.21,0:22:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't scan something so large.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.60,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We did learn a lot from tonight, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.66,0:22:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:34.17,0:22:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone survived.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.73,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most important thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.06,0:22:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.69,0:22:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:43.18,0:22:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.34,0:22:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we planned?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.54,0:22:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.52,0:22:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme ask this again, Ushio.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:51.20,0:22:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya cut that link to Haine, will it really be safe?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.35,0:22:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked with Rose and Gil.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I tweak their minds a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They basically just gotta be like me.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.52,0:23:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We could easily kill it right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.82,0:23:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya sure, Mio?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:11.59,0:23:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Sis.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.77,0:23:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Make my shadow our ally.
